title: All Employees: Service-Providing in Middlesex-Monmouth-Ocean, NJ
notes: Middlesex-Monmouth-Ocean, NJ constitutes a significant percentage of the state's total statewide employment. This series is calculated in addition to the New York-Wayne-White Plains, NY-NJ (MD)'s statistics because of it's importance to the state. For more details on non-standard area definitions, visit the additional resources (https://www.bls.gov/sae/additional-resources/non-standard-ces-areas.htm) of the Current Employment Statistics.
